name: Barbieri Orthodontics
overview:
Barbieri Orthodontics is one of the best orthodontic offices serving the greater Nashville, TN, area. Dr. Damon Barbieri and his staff employ state of the art technology to tailor treatments according to each individual patient’s needs.Dr. Barbieri prides himself on creating and maintaining the best smiles in Tennessee through an undying attention to detail and passion for excellence.

Services Offered: Braces, Clear Braces, Invisalign, TMJ/TMD Treatment, Children’s Braces, Teen Braces, Damon Braces

Brands Carried: Invisalign, Damon Braces

Professional Associations: Middle Tennessee Society for Advanced Dentistry, The Progressive Orthodontist Study Club, Millennium Study Club, American Association of Orthodontists, Tennessee Dental Association, Nashville Dental Society

Payment Options: Credit, debit, cash, check, no interest financing, CareCredit

Hours: M-Th 8:30-5
Friday (emergency only) 8:30-12
